subject: TestCollector not supported on this platform.
msgSnippet: Hi, I am using Junit for testing and it works very well on one platform, when I move it to another machine (Windows 2000) I get No Test Cases found check
messageBody:
Hi,

I am using Junit for testing and it works very well on one platform,
when I move it to another machine (Windows 2000) I get "No Test Cases
found" check TestCollector is supported on this platform..

Does anybody have any ideas why I would get this error, why would a
TestCollector not work on a certain platform..

This may be down to a simple configuration issue as I am relatively
inexperienced with Junit.

Thanks in advance.

Dave
